)	O
.	O

As	O
can	O
be	O
seen	O
from	O
FIG	O
.	O
2	O
,	O
correction	O
system	O
204	O
is	O
a	O
character-based	O
correction	O
system	O
.	O
This	O
means	O
that	O
correction	O
system	O
204	O
enables	O
or	O
allows	O
the	O
user	O
to	O
correct	O
