on	O
a	O
character-by-character	O
basis	O
.	O
When	O
correction	O
system	O
204	O
is	O
an	O
alphabetic	O
language	O
correction	O
system	O
,	O
the	O
characters	O
refer	O
to	O
the	O
letters	O
(	O
or	O
alphabets	O
)	O
of	O
the	O
word	O
.	O

Correction	O
system	O
204	O
can	O
be	O
implemented	O
by	O
a	O
software	O
module	O
running	O
on	O
processor	O
102	O
of	O
FIG	O
.	O
1	O
,	O
by	O
a	O
hardware	O
integrated	O
circuit	O
or	O
by	O
a	O
combination	O
of	O
software	O
and	O
hardware	O
.	O
Correction	O
system	O
204	O
allows	O
for	O
in-word	O
propagation	O
of	O
the	O
correction	O
of	O
a	O
character	O
throughout	O
the	O
word	O
that	O
contains	O
the	O
character	O
.	O
In	O
addition	O
,	O
correction	O
system	O
204	O
allows	O
for	O
between-word	O
propagation	O
of	O
the	O
correction	O
of	O
a	O
word	O
throughout	O
a	O
sentence	O
or	O
text	O
.	O
The	O
in-word	O
propagation	O
and	O
between-word	O
propagation	O
adjusts	O
the	O
N-best	O
list	O
for	O
subsequent	O
characters	O
or	O
words	O
as	O
a	O
