easier	O
for	O
users	O
to	O
make	O
choices	O
.	O

Finally	O
,	O
character-based	O
selections	O
are	O
able	O
to	O
compose	O
much	O
more	O
character	O
combinations	O
than	O
word-based	O
selections	O
.	O
Character-based	O
error	O
correction	O
allows	O
the	O
user	O
to	O
make	O
up	O
a	O
word	O
not	O
