list	O
.	O
This	O
can	O
occur	O
if	O
the	O
user	O
speaks	O
a	O
word	O
that	O
is	O
not	O
in	O
the	O
active	O
vocabulary	O
.	O

Briefly	O
,	O
the	O
operation	O
of	O
correction	O
system	O
204	O
is	O
now	O
described	O
as	O
follows	O
.	O
The	O
user	O
first	O
scans	O
through	O
the	O
text	O
(	O
e.g.	O
sequentially	O
scanning	O
through	O
the	O
text	O
)	O
and	O
finds	O
the	O
first	O
erroneous	O
character	O
(	O
e.g.	O
the	O
left-most	O
erroneous	O
character	O
on	O
a	O
given	O
line	O
of	O
text	O
)	O
By	O
using	O
cursor	O
control	O
device	O
123	O
,	O
keyboard	O
and/or	O
voice	O
command	O
to	O
point	O
to	O
the	O
character	O
,	O
