words	O
subsequent	O
to	O
the	O
changed	O
word	O
based	O
on	O
the	O
acoustic	O
matching	O
score	O
,	O
the	O
unigram	O
probability	O
score	O
,	O
and	O
the	O
long	O
distance	O
